---
title: "SeedImbibed"
output: html_document
---


This event is raised when germination occurs by [GerminatingPhase](/docs/Models/PMF/Phenology/Phases/GerminatingPhase.qmd), signaling other models or processes to begin their activities related to the germinated seed.



## Triggering

This event is triggered in the [Clock](/docs/Models/PMF/Phenology/Phases/GerminatingPhase.qmd) model.
